15:50.650 --> 15:52.903
Well, I'm allergic
to over 300 plants and spices,

15:52.904 --> 15:54.030
so don't get too comfortable.

15:54.031 --> 15:55.199
Oh, cool, I've never ridden

15:55.200 --> 15:56.703
in an ambulance before.

15:56.704 --> 15:58.205
Oh, no, I can't afford an ambulance,

15:58.206 --> 16:00.544
