16:37.201 --> 16:39.956
No, no, I want my fucking battenberg!

16:44.381 --> 16:46.886
Oh, fuck, now they're playing music.

16:46.887 --> 16:48.890
"Für Elise."

16:48.891 --> 16:50.309
