17:35.150 --> 17:36.569
No, totally.

17:36.570 --> 17:38.573
It just all feels so random, though.

17:38.574 --> 17:39.950
It's like, for all we know,
God's just some

17:39.951 --> 17:41.328
M. Night Shyamalan asshole

17:41.329 --> 17:42.496
