18:47.670 --> 18:48.963
Sure. Yeah.

18:48.964 --> 18:50.925
It was really nice seeing you, Mom.

18:50.926 --> 18:53.013
And thank you, again, for dinner.

18:53.014 --> 18:54.307
- My God.
- Oh...

18:54.308 --> 18:56.729
Um, if you want...

18:56.730 --> 18:58.315
and I'm sure you have a place to stay,

18:58.316 --> 19:01.071
