your bedroom's always open,

19:01.072 --> 19:03.116
and I have a laundry machine.

19:03.117 --> 19:05.371
I know. And a dryer too.

19:07.417 --> 19:10.130
But seriously, you're good?

19:10.131 --> 19:11.842
I am good, yeah.

19:11.843 --> 19:12.844
Okay.

19:12.845 --> 19:14.848
Well...

19:14.849 --> 19:16.226
- I love you.
- I love you too, Mom.

19:16.227 --> 19:19.149
I am so happy you're home.

19:20.276 --> 19:22.280
- Okay.
- Okay. Bye.

19:34.012 --> 19:36.141
Hey, Rae?

19:36.142 --> 19:38.604
I'm starting an earthquake kit.

19:38.605 --> 19:40.900
I was thinking...

19:40.901 --> 19:43.990
calamity could strike at any moment,

19:43.991 --> 19:46.077
and we need to be prepared.

19:46.078 --> 19:48.416
Also, have I mentioned recently
that I love you?

19:49.627 --> 19:50.754
Hi.

19:52.550 --> 19:55.220
- Hi.
- I'm Jeff.

19:55.221 --> 19:57.266
- Jeff.
- Uh-huh. Rae's boyfriend.

19:57.267 --> 20:00.189
- Oh.
- Hey, guys.

20:00.190 --> 20:02.986
- How was dinner?
- Good.

20:02.987 --> 20:05.032
What is this?

20:05.033 --> 20:06.744
Earthquake kit. Can we talk?

20:06.745 --> 20:08.789
Uh, yeah.

20:08.790 --> 20:10.544
