20:27.369 --> 20:28.829
Is that you?

20:32.588 --> 20:37.639
Hey, I do not masturbate in the dark.

20:37.640 --> 20:39.476
It's called mood lighting.

20:41.773 --> 20:44.611
And...

20:44.612 --> 20:48.368
I'm ready for that secret now, so...

20:48.369 --> 20:51.165
whenever you're ready,
just lay it on me,

20:51.166 --> 20:55.758
'cause happiness...

20:55.759 --> 20:57.637
here I come.

20:57.638 --> 20:59.348
No Bluetooth detected.

20:59.349 --> 21:02.187
You will arrive at your
destination in 14 minutes.

21:15.425 --> 21:16.926
Sonja?

21:23.189 --> 21:24.692
Sonja?

21:26.571 --> 21:28.533
