21:36.508 --> 21:38.385
Whatcha doing?

21:38.386 --> 21:40.723
- I'm breaking in.
- Okay.

21:40.724 --> 21:43.144
I mean, it's animal abuse,
what she's doing.

21:43.145 --> 21:45.692
Well, that may be, but...

21:45.693 --> 21:47.361
