21:47.362 --> 21:49.658
I mean, doubt it. They know us.

21:49.659 --> 21:51.327
Can you not say "us"?

21:51.328 --> 21:53.373
'Cause I'm kind of having a night,

21:53.374 --> 21:58.843
and, uh, don't really want to
